{"tid":1564172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"義士們請進","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:09:40.000Z","uid":273926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7711368ca3bb6a10f25dceabee4aeaa6fb5a7284","tid":1564172,"uid":273926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"抱歉小弟P牌，<br />\n<br />\n在此想討論一些事，各位義士各區行動時，可以盡量即場商量安排手足做攝影隊伍，拍住活動全程/拍實其他潛在危險地方，雖然好似同記者重疊工作咁有點on9，但是記者朋友的鏡頭有時候都是有限，Cover唔哂所有野。<br />\n<br />\n我留意到好多各區活動都有藍絲用不同方法襲擊人，剛剛新鮮滾熱辣有人鴨脷洲淋鏹水，平時十點屋村叫口號行動有人掟水彈或其他雜物，有人持刀想斬大叫的手足等。如果我地一直有自己人鏡頭，影實掟水彈的樓上/ 活動過程。施襲者就無得偷雞。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？"},{"pid":"91e0fc97d80133dc8c4136a82d9ac0e93e500617","tid":1564172,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9837c5c93c2cbf54e6402cc8711d2256ab59d3ff","tid":1564172,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}